Zhao Zhiguo was in pain and almost didn't chew the mud. When he turned around, he realized it was Zhao Ziming, staring at him with angry eyes.



"I... I want to try a gun..." Zhao Zhiguo stammered.



Whether on the training ground or the battlefield, obey orders, Zhao Zhiguo's squad leader told him on the first day he joined the army.
